data.description: Experience the ultimate blend of natural beauty and urban convenience at our breathtaking riverfront property. Nestled on over 7.5 acres of land, this stunning location offers the best of both worlds. Discover tranquility and serenity in the picturesque surroundings, while enjoying the modern comfort of a beautifully designed manufactured home. With its prime position at the edge of city limits, you'll relish the peace and privacy while still being just moments away from all the amenities and attractions that city living has to offer. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own your own slice of paradise!
